(196, 2, 'Sami Kubo', 'sami@reelgrrls.org', 'http://www.reelgrrls.org', '67.160.64.147', '2009-03-03 21:30:03', '2009-03-04 05:30:03', 'Hello, I am an intern with Reel Grrls, a local non-profit organization that empowers young women through teaching filmmaking and media literacy. The staff and mentors of Reel Grrls are competing in the Hot Docs International Documentary Challenge where we create a documentary in 5 days. We may be interested in doing this documentary on the Seattle DIY scene, and I was wondering if there was someone from the SeattleDIY Collective who would be willing to be interviewed by us. We will be making the documentary this weekend, so I apologize for the late notice. However, we are still unsure if DIY will be the topic because it is dependent on the theme of the Doc Challenge, which we will hear on Thursday (3/5). At this point, I am wondering if you would be interested in some kind of participation. Thank you,', 0, '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; U; Intel Mac OS X; en) AppleWebKit/523.12 (KHTML, like Gecko) Version/3.0.4 Safari/523.12', '', 0, 0),
