dia.blubrry.com/wordpresspodcast/media.rawvoice.com/seorockstars/www2.webmasterradio.fm/mp3/wordpresspodcast/10/WP062210.mp3";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:11;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:77:"\n         \n         \n         \n         \n         \n         \n         \n      ";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:4:{s:0:"";a:5:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:48:"Yoast: SEOktoberfest 2010: looking forward to it";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:58:"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/joostdevalk/~3/oE7FH92Q3XM/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:903:"<p>Marcus just posted the trailer to SEOktoberfest 2010, and it&#39;s going to be another awesome edition of this epic conference / party / network event. I wasn&#39;t there last year (my daughter was about to be born, seems a valid excuse) but I&#39;ll definitely be there this year! Check out the trailer: You&#39;ve seen it [...]</p><p><a rel="nofollow"\n target="_blank" href="http://yoast.com/seoktoberfest-2010/">SEOktoberfest 2010: looking forward to it</a> is a post from <a rel="nofollow"\n target="_blank" href="http://yoast.com/about-me/">Joost de Valk</a>&#39;s <a rel="nofollow"\n target="_blank" href="http://yoast.com">Yoast - Tweaking Websites</a>.A good WordPress blog needs good hosting, you don&#39;t want your blog to be slow, or, even worse, down, do you? Check out my thoughts on <a rel="nofollow"\n target="_blank" href="http://yoast.com/wordpress-hosting/">WordPress hosting</a>!</p>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:24:"http://yoast.com/?p=2693";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s