dropping in a shortcode like [twitter-widget username="xavisys"] to embed a widget like this:</p><div\nclass="widget_twitter"><div><br\n/><h2><a\nclass="twitterwidget twitterwidget-title" title="Twitter: xavisys" href="http://twitter.com/xavisys">Tweets from Xavisys</a></h2><p><ul><li><span\nclass=''entry-content''><a\nhref="http://twitter.com/springloops" class="twitter-user">@springloops</a> Having a deployment issue.  E-Mail sent to support@springloops.com with details.</span> <span\nclass=''entry-meta''><span\nclass=''time-meta''><a\nhref="http://twitter.com/xavisys/statuses/16426252529">12:04:54 AM June 18, 2010</a></span> <span\nclass=''from-meta''>from <a\nhref="http://www.seesmic.com/" rel="nofollow">Seesmic</a></span><span\nclass="in-reply-to-meta"><a\nhref="http://twitter.com/springloops/statuses/" class="reply-to">in reply to springloops</a></span></span></li><li><span\nclass=''entry-content''>WordPress 3.0 has been released! It''s so fresh it''s still propagating across servers <a\nhref="http://bit.ly/aCsHET">http://bit.ly/aCsHET</a> <a\nhref="http://search.twitter.com/search?q=%23wordpress" class="twitter-hashtag">#wordpress</a></span> <span\nclass=''entry-meta''><span\nclass=''time-meta''><a\nhref="http://twitter.com/xavisys/statuses/16400649077">04:20:44 PM June 17, 2010</a></span> <span\nclass=''from-meta''>from <a\nhref="http://www.seesmic.com/" rel="nofollow">Seesmic</a></span></span></li></ul></div></div><p><p>To read more about how to use the shortcodes and to download the plugin, go to the <a\nhref="http://xavisys.com/wordpress-plugins/wordpress-twitter-widget/">Twitter Widget Pro</a> page.  For support, go to the <a\nhref="http://xavisys.com/support/forum/twitter-widget-pro/">Twitter Widget Pro Forum</a><br\n/><h3 class=''related_post_title''>Related Posts:</h3><ul\nclass=''related_post''><li><a\nhref=''http://xavisys.com/10-great-wordpress-plugins/'' title=''10 Great WordPress Plugins''>10 Great WordPress Plugins</a></li><li><a\nhref=''http://