(73, 3, '2008-12-16 05:38:39', '2008-12-16 11:38:39', 'Here are some websites the address local food justice issues: \r\n\r\nCommunity Alliance for Global Justice - Food Justice Project:\r\n<a href="http://http://www.seattleglobaljustice.org/food-justice/">http://www.seattleglobaljustice.org/food-justice/</a>\r\n\r\nSeattle Permaculture Guild: This site is meant to be a gathering point for folks in Seattle wanting to practice, play with, and learn more about Permaculture.\r\n<a href="http://http://seattlepermacultureguild.org/">http://seattlepermacultureguild.org/</a>\r\nPermaculture wiki: <a href="http://http://seattlepermacultureguild.org/wiki/wiki.php?n=Main.HomePage">http://seattlepermacultureguild.org/wiki/wiki.php?n=Main.HomePage</a>\r\n\r\nSolid Ground - Marra Farm: Marra Farm is a model urban community farm engaging people in sustainable agriculture and education while enhancing local food security. Tucked into the South Park neighborhood of Seattle, it has 4 acres of historic preserved farmland. \r\n<a href="http://http://www.solid-ground.org/Programs/Nutrition/Marra/Pages/default.aspx">\r\nhttp://www.solid-ground.org/Programs/Nutrition/Marra/Pages/default.aspx</a>\r\n\r\nCascadia Food Not Lawns:\r\n<a href="http://www.foodnotlawns.com/">http://www.foodnotlawns.com/</a>\r\n\r\nGuerrilla Gardening:\r\nhttp://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Guerrilla_gardening\r\nhttp://www.laguerrillagardening.org/\r\nbooks on guerrilla gardening:\r\nhttp://www.newsociety.com/bookid/3945\r\nhttp://www.amazon.co.uk/Guerrilla-Gardening-Handbook-without-Boundaries/dp/0747590818\r\n\r\nSeed Bombs:\r\nhttp://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Seed_bombing\r\nrecipe: http://www.carbonsmart.com/carboncopy/2008/03/seed-bombs-for.html\r\n\r\n', 'Food Justice', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'food-justice', '', '', '2008-12-19 16:57:07', '2008-12-20 00:57:07', '', 71, 'http://www.seattlediy.com/new/?page_id=73', 0, 'page', '', 0),
