ct</strong>\r\n<strong>The Bikery</strong>\r\n<strong>Winter Skillshare</strong>\r\n<strong>For Crying Out Loud</strong>', 'Seattle DIY Collective''s projects', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '109-revision-2', '', '', '2008-12-16 20:52:32', '2008-12-17 04:52:32', '', 109, 'http://www.seattlediy.com/?p=111', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
