(159, 11, '2008-12-17 21:39:36', '2008-12-18 05:39:36', 'Here are some websites the address local food justice issues: \r\n\r\nCommunity Alliance for Global Justice - Food Justice Project:\r\n<a href="http://">http://www.seattleglobaljustice.org/food-justice/</a>\r\n\r\nSeattle Permaculture Guild: This site is meant to be a gathering point for folks in Seattle wanting to practice, play with, and learn more about Permaculture.\r\n<a href="http://">http://seattlepermacultureguild.org/\r\n - http://seattlepermacultureguild.org/wiki/wiki.php?n</a>\r\n\r\nSolid Ground - Marra Farm: Marra Farm is a model urban community farm engaging people in sustainable agriculture and education while enhancing local food security. Tucked into the South Park neighborhood of Seattle, it has 4 acres of historic preserved farmland. \r\n<a href="http://">\r\nhttp://www.solid-ground.org/Programs/Nutrition/Marra/Pages/default.aspx</a>\r\n', 'Food Justice', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '73-revision-4', '', '', '2008-12-17 21:39:36', '2008-12-18 05:39:36', '', 73, 'http://www.seattlediy.com/?p=159', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(160, 11, '2008-12-17 21:41:00', '2008-12-18 05:41:00', 'Here are some websites the address local food justice issues: \r\n\r\nCommunity Alliance for Global Justice - Food Justice Project:\r\n<a href="http://">http://www.seattleglobaljustice.org/food-justice/</a>\r\n\r\nSeattle Permaculture Guild: This site is meant to be a gathering point for folks in Seattle wanting to practice, play with, and learn more about Permaculture.\r\n<a href="http://">http://">http://seattlepermacultureguild.org/</a>\r\n - <a href="http://">http://seattlepermacultureguild.org/wiki/wiki.php?n</a>\r\n\r\nSolid Ground - Marra Farm: Marra Farm is a model urban community farm engaging people in sustainable agriculture and education while enhancing local food security. Tucked into the South Park neighborhood of Seattle, it has 4 acres of historic preserved farmland. \r\n<a href="http://">\r\nhttp://www.solid-ground.org/Programs/Nutrition/Marra/Pages/default.aspx</a>\r\n', 'Food Justice', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '73-revision-5', '', '', '2008-12-17 21:41:00', '2008-12-18 05:41:00', '', 73, 'http://www.seattlediy.com/?p=160', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
