ingham, Seattle, Tacoma, Olympia and Portland.” They''ve thusfar published several newsletters about regional, national, and global issues and helped put on a speaking tour. For more info go to <a href="http://nwcommonaction.org">http://nwcommonaction.org</a>', 'January 2009 news!', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '209-autosave', '', '', '2009-01-03 00:06:52', '2009-01-03 08:06:52', '', 209, 'http://www.seattlediy.com/?p=211', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
