(216, 1, '2009-01-23 15:48:29', '2009-01-23 23:48:29', 'Hey friends,\r\nWe''re going to be working on putting out the February SeattleDIY Community Newsletter, and we need any news about the community or things that affect the community. We distribute about 500 of the newsletters every month around town, so it''s a great opportunity to let people know about exciting things going on, or put a call out for help or participation, and is a good way to keep us all informed and connected. Email any news you might have to sdiycollective (a) gmail (*) com!\r\n\r\nAlso, we just filmed some stuff to make a trailer for the upcoming Riot Grrl Karaoke (http://www.myspace.com/riotgrrlkaraoke) that we''re doing in February. We''re wanting to film more stuff and also get videos of things that other people in the community are doing, and share them on this website.\r\n\r\nWant to get involved with helping us out with these projects? Come to our next meeting! Meetings happen every Sunday at 6pm. \r\n1st Sundays: Something Wonderful\r\n2nd Sundays: <a href="http://www.myspace.com/newcrompton">New Crompton</a>\r\n3rd Sundays: <a href="http://myspace.com/healthytimesfunclub">Healthy Times Fun Club</a>\r\nLast Sundays: <a href="http://myspace.com/dancylvaniahouse">Dancylvania</a>', 'February Newsletter! Cool stuff coming up!', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'february-newsletter-cool-stuff-coming-up', '', '', '2009-01-23 15:48:29', '2009-01-23 23:48:29', '', 0, 'http://www.seattlediy.com/?p=216', 0, 'post', '', 0),
