(265, 96, '2009-04-06 12:56:02', '2009-04-06 20:56:02', '<p>When I first heard the band James Rabbit everything I previously understood about what making music is all about changed. When I first heard that I would be setting up a show for them at my house I new that I had to find a way to convince everybody I knew to come to see the show. So please allow me to tell you a little bit about James Rabbit and why they are one of my favorite bands. </p>\n\n<p>James Rabbit makes music that is almost indescribable. After allot of discussion with my roommates we came up with a few bands to compare them too, Queen, The Dirty Projectors, Laurie Anderson, Electric Light Orchestra, Half Japanese, and George Gershwin, but that hardly describes what you will see at this show. We are talking giant heartbreaking singalongs, ridiculously high energy performance, and inspiring spoken word that is bound to unravel the most stubborn of concert goers. </p>\n\n<p>Here are some videos to help convince you...</p>\n\n<p>&lt;object width="445" height="364"&gt;&lt;param name="movie" value="http://www.youtube.com/v/6OoGa9vkLbY&amp;hl=en&amp;fs=1&amp;color1=0x234900&amp;color2=0x4e9e00&amp;border=1"&gt;&lt;/param&gt;&lt;param name="allowFullScreen" value="true"&gt;&lt;/param&gt;&lt;param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always"&gt;&lt;/param&gt;&lt;embed src="http://www.youtube.com/v/6OoGa9vkLbY&amp;hl=en&amp;fs=1&amp;color1=0x234900&amp;color2=0x4e9e00&amp;border=1" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" allowscriptaccess="always" allowfullscreen="true" width="445" height="364"&gt;&lt;/embed&gt;&lt;/object&gt;</p>\n\n<p>&lt;object width="445" height="364"&gt;&lt;param name="movie" value="http://www.youtube.com/v/zpDaMiUR-YY&amp;hl=en&amp;fs=1&amp;color1=0x006699&amp;color2=0x54abd6&amp;border=1"&gt;&lt;/param&gt;&lt;param name="allowFullScreen" value="true"&gt;&lt;/param&gt;&lt;param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always"&gt;&lt;/param&gt;&lt;embed src="http://www.youtube.com/v/zpDaMiUR-YY&amp;hl