(284, 96, '2009-05-07 23:08:01', '2009-05-08 07:08:01', '<p>Splinter Cake is this dude named Kelly. Kelly and I both used to live in Phoenix Arizona. I have seen Splinter Cake live a ton of times and everyone has been completely different. Sometimes playing by himself on an acoustic guitar singing mountain goats-esque folk punk. Sometimes playing with a full band and performing poppy spoken word in the style of Half Japanese. One time he performed a whole set of solo black metal in full corpse paint. I have no idea what Kelly is going to do at my house tomorrow night but it might be sort of like this...<br />\r\n<object width="560" height="340"><param name="movie" value="http://www.youtube.com/v/2lv93nQI0-Q&hl=en&fs=1"></param><param name="allowFullScreen" value="true"></param><param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always"></param><embed src="http://www.youtube.com/v/2lv93nQI0-Q&hl=en&fs=1" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" allowscriptaccess="always" allowfullscreen="true" width="560" height="340"></embed></object><object width="560" height="340"><param name="movie" value="http://www.youtube.com/v/8ptyn_NTN8w&hl=en&fs=1"></param><param name="allowFullScreen" value="true"></param><param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always"></param><embed src="http://www.youtube.com/v/8ptyn_NTN8w&hl=en&fs=1" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" allowscriptaccess="always" allowfullscreen="true" width="560" height="340"></embed></object></p>\r\n<p>You have probably already seen World History and Elephant Kiss? play but they are both amazing. </p>\r\n<p>World History is one of my favorite bands. It''s sort of like Neutral Milk Hotel but better. Seriously. </p>\r\n<p>Elephant Kiss? combines glitchy electronics, indie pop, and old school feel good hip hop. </p>\r\n<p>Let''s get serious you guys come on! </p>\r\n<p>New Crompton.<br />\r\n4711 12th Ave NE<br />\r\nFriday May 8th (tonight!)<br />\r\n8:00 Good show!<br />\r\nNo drinks dude.</p>\r\n', 'Splinter Cake, World History, Elephant Kiss? @ New Crompton', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'splinter-cake-world-history-elephant-kiss-new-crompton', '', '', '2009-05-07 23:08:01', '2009-05-08 07:08:01', '', 0, 'http://www.seattlediy.com/?p=284', 0, 'post', '', 0),
