(415, 98, '2009-07-31 17:44:54', '2009-08-01 01:44:54', '<p>This is a very last-minute show <em>but</em> it is worth it if you go. It''s <strong>Monday, the 3rd of August</strong>, This upcoming Monday.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Personally, I have only seen the Bash Brothers play but not the Apollo Ghosts or the Madonna Bangers. They''re on a small tour in the states from the fair country from above, Canadia.  It''s going to probably be punk-as-eff, so bring your earplugs so let''s welcome them with hugs and kisses.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I met the Bash Brothers through Angelo Spencer afnd a inversely sold out show at the Comet Tavern. I was upset but, you know... the Comet. It was a great show though! Desolation Wilderness and Generifus were also playing so it was kind of upsetting that no one was there. I mean, I guess it made sense because the academy awards were <em>that night</em>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Tangent</strong>: Do you ever notice about how there are a lot of actors that are <em>incredibly</em> poor at presenting themselves at the AA''s? They''re actors... I mean, come on! They should be good at <em>acting</em> excited about getting an award!</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Anyway</em>, Kristjanne and Lindsay (the Bash Brothers), Angelo  and I were chumming it up, like we do. Then when were were talking about how much we really like Angelo''s music after he was done, the BB''s went to set up and as they started playing... I pooped myself.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Not</em> the bad pooping either, the good kind that your heart does when it falls in love with something unexpectedly. A metaphorical poop, I guess.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Apollo Ghosts:<br />\r\n <a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.myspace.com/adrianteacher" target="_blank">http://www.myspace.com/adrianteacher</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bash Brothers:<br />\r\n <a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.myspace.com/bashbashbash" target="_blank">http://www.myspace.com/bashbashbash</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Madonna Bangers:<br />\r\n <a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.myspace.com/themadonnabangers" target="_blank">http://www.myspace.com/themadonnabangers</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Love,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Kenneth-</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="padding-left: 30px"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style="padding-left: 30px">"THESE MIGHT VERY WELL BE THE BEST BANDS YOU SEE THIS SUMMER.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>seriously. I cannot recommend them highly enough. also, RAD DUDES."</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="padding-left: 30px">-Jenn H.-</p>', 'Apollo Ghosts, Bash Brothers, Madonna Bangers @ New Crompton', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '395-revision-9', '', '', '2009-07-31 17:44:54', '2009-08-01 01:44:54', '', 395, 'http://www.seattlediy.com/?p=415', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
