(440, 99, '2009-08-07 14:13:23', '2009-08-07 22:13:23', '<img src="http://i13.photobucket.com/albums/a290/geoshmuck/www072.jpg" alt="null" />\r\n\r\nThere''s going to be an AMAZING show this Sunday, WITH:\r\nBad Weather California (CO)------&gt;badweathercalifornia.blogspot.com\r\ntheir tropical, pop-rock is going to make this one of the best shows of the summer!\r\nyou''ve seen them play back-up for daniel johnston and tour with dirty projectors and akron family, now watch them in the cozy setting of a house-show!!!!!! it''s going to be WONDERFUL!!\r\n\r\nJordan O''Jordan (OLY)-----&gt;myspace.com/jordanojordanmusic\r\njordan''s sweet croons and poetic lyrics are going to melt your heart and get your foot tapping, wishing he would hum his sweet melodies for us until the end of TIME! he is the biggest sweetheart in the world, and you will be singing his songs to yourself for days!!\r\n\r\nWe''re going to have free vegan food around 8, and the show will start around 9!! \r\nWe''ll have a huge free market set up on our front porch, where you can pick up our recycled fashions and play dress-up! \r\nCOME HANG OUT WITH US!!  on the 131, 60, 174 bus-lines!\r\nwww.arcticcirclehouse.info\r\n', 'SHOW THIS SUNDAY @ ARCTIC CIRCLE!', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'show-this-sunday-arctic-circle', '', '', '2009-08-07 14:13:23', '2009-08-07 22:13:23', '', 0, 'http://www.seattlediy.com/?p=440', 0, 'post', '', 0),
