(447, 1, '2009-08-10 10:22:28', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '<img src="http://c1.ac-images.myspacecdn.com/images02/67/l_88d168c9428749b4b9061a54b0baaff0.jpg" alt="show at the greenhouse" />\n\nI find shows like this really exciting - a crap load of bands, all approaching their music from different angles, yet somehow fitting so well on a bill together. Night Train, for example, spawned from the awesome "Hot Grits" performance - an all Black, all female garage punk band who are fun and dancy, while Purple Rhinestone Eagle are also an all-female band who bust out shredding epic metal. The common threads between these bands may not seem immediately noticeable, but they''re none the less there. Ex\n\nMonday, August 10th @ the Greenhouse!\n\nPurple Rhinestone Eagle (PDX)\nTelepathic Liberation Army\nCaucus (JPN)\nHerr Jazz\nGenerifus (OLY)\nNight Train\n\nDoors @ 7:30pm.\nShow @ 8:15pm.\n\nALL-AGES!\n$5 suggested donation!\n\nGREENHOUSE!\n2515 S. Charles St.\nCENTRAL DISTRICT SEATTLE!', 'rad show at the Greenhouse', 0, '', 'draft', 'open', 'open', '', '', '', '', '2009-08-10 10:22:28', '2009-08-10 18:22:28', '', 0, 'http://www.seattlediy.com/?p=447', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(448, 1, '2009-08-10 12:32:41', '2009-08-10 20:32:41', '<img src="http://c1.ac-images.myspacecdn.com/images02/67/l_88d168c9428749b4b9061a54b0baaff0.jpg" alt="show at the greenhouse" />\r\n\r\nI find shows like this really exciting - a crap load of bands, all approaching their music from different angles, yet somehow fitting so well on a bill together. For example, Night Train spawned from the awesome "Hot Grits" performance - an all Black, all female garage punk band who are fun and dancy, while Purple Rhinestone Eagle are also an all-female band who bust out shredding epic metal. The common threads between these bands may not seem immediately noticeable, but they''re none the less there. Expect this show to feel almost more like a celebration than a typical rock show, as we witness a convergence of different ideas and musical expressions squarely in one of the most beloved DIY show spaces in Seattle. \r\n\r\nMonday, August 10th @ the Greenhouse!\r\n\r\nPurple Rhinestone Eagle (PDX)\r\nTelepathic Liberation Army\r\nCaucus (JPN)\r\nHerr Jazz\r\nGenerifus (OLY)\r\nNight Train\r\n\r\nDoors @ 7:30pm. Show @ 8:15pm. ALL-AGES! $5 suggested donation!\r\nGREENHOUSE! // 2515 S. Charles St. // CENTRAL DISTRICT SEATTLE!', 'rad show at the greenhouse, tonight! 8/10/09', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'rad-show-at-the-greenhouse-tonight-81009', '', '', '2009-08-10 12:32:41', '2009-08-10 20:32:41', '', 0, 'http://www.seattlediy.com/?p=448', 0, 'post', '', 0),
