direct action</a>, promoting a form of <a href="http://www.insurgentdesire.org.uk/notes.htm">insurrectionary anarchism</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br class="spacer_" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can read it for <a href="http://tarnac9.wordpress.com/texts/the-coming-insurrection/">free here</a>, or picking up your own copy at the benefit from the Tout Niquer distro. (If you cannot attend but still want a print copy, they are also available at <a href="http://www.leftbankbooks.com/store/?&amp;cookieSet=1">Left Bank Books</a>.)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>MUSIC TBA.</strong> Let''s hang out!</p>', 'FRIDAY: TARNAC 9 BENEFIT AT ARCTIC CIRCLE', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '472-revision-6', '', '', '2009-08-17 22:22:12', '2009-08-18 06:22:12', '', 472, 'http://www.seattlediy.com/?p=478', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
