(506, 99, '2009-09-18 11:03:42', '2009-09-18 19:03:42', '<p><strong>The <a href="http://www.seattleanarchist.org/">Seattle Anarchist Bookfair</a> is less than a month away!  We are so excited!</strong></p>\r\n<p>(October 17th-18th at the Underground Events Center, 2407 1st Ave)</p>\r\n<p>Today, we updated the <a href="http://www.seattleanarchist.org/?page_id=51">list of projects that are tabling</a> and posted our <a href="http://www.seattleanarchist.org/?page_id=62">most up-to-date workshops/panels list.</a></p>\r\n<p>Also, we’ve been asked by a few people if we have a HOUSING / RIDE BOARD.  Well, <a href="https://we.riseup.net/seattlebookfair">we do now</a>. To participate in it, head over to <a href="http://we.riseup.net">riseup.net and set up a crabgrass account</a>.  It’s quick and simple–if you’re not familiar with Crabgrass, its’ kind of like an anti-corporate social-networking site run by radicals.  Sign up for an account, and then post on our housing/ride board pages if you need or can provide either.</p>\r\n<p>Finally, if you have any questions about anything–including how and why we are organizing the bookfair and benefits–please get directly in touch: seattleanarchistbookfair at riseup.net</p>\r\n', 'Anarchist Bookfair in Less Than One Month', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '506', '', 'http://www.seattleanarchist.org/?page_id=51\nhttp://www.seattleanarchist.org/?page_id=62', '2009-09-18 13:22:19', '2009-09-18 21:22:19', '', 0, 'http://www.seattlediy.com/?p=506', 0, 'post', '', 0),
