(514, 11, '2009-09-24 21:59:46', '2009-09-25 05:59:46', 'Please join us on Saturday, September 26 at 4:30pm for an infoshop meeting. \r\n\r\nWe will be meeting from 4:30-5:00pm at Pilot Books, 219 Broadway E (upstairs). Pilot Books will be where the infoshop will be housed. For those who have not met Summer or seen the space we thought that this would be a great opportunity to do so. \r\n\r\nThen we will meet at a collective house a block away by the name of Dancylvania, 110 Harvard Ave. E. We will be here from 5-7:30pm. (If the doors are locked please ring the doorbell which is on the left side of the door) This will be the real nitty gritty time of the meeting. We will be really getting serious about what we want it to look like, timelines, different models, etc. \r\n\r\nTo help get us through the meeting we are having a potluck. So, if you will be joining us try and bring a dish to share. This is a vegan house so please make a vegan dish to share. \r\n\r\nCannot wait to see you all for this amazing meeting to create an even more amazing space!', 'Meeting for Infoshop this Saturday', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'meeting-for-infoshop-this-saturday', '', '', '2009-09-24 21:59:46', '2009-09-25 05:59:46', '', 0, 'http://www.seattlediy.com/?p=514', 0, 'post', '', 0),
