(521, 98, '2009-09-28 00:04:03', '2009-09-28 08:04:03', '<p><img style="vertical-align: middle" src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2484/3902651655_de409fe251.jpg" alt="" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hey Everyone!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You know how cool last minute show promotions are? They''re the best kinds of cool!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Here''s why: Originally, you thought to yourself, "What the deuce can I do with my life on a Monday night?" but now you think (and quite possibly yell aloud) "I''m going to a potluck on Monday among friends (and future friends)!"</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This evening (of this fairest Monday) there will be a potluck at the New Crompton in the U-District starting at 7:00. There will also be four acts performing. Manners from Massachusettes with their traveling compadre, Brian S. Ellis. There will also be wonderful local acts Pet Dander and Temple Vibe performing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This should be a fun gathering. What''s great about potlucks? Is <em>you</em> make them great by bringing great food (think vegitarian / vegan)!</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n		<li><strong>Manners</strong> (on tour from Massachusetts): <a href="http://www.myspace.com/mnnrs" target="_blank">myspace.com/mnnrs</a></li>\r\n		<li><strong>B</strong><strong>rian S Ellis</strong> (on tour with Manners): <a href="http://www.myspace.com/brianstephenellis" target="_blank">myspace.com/brianstephenellis</a></li>\r\n		<li><strong>Pet Dander</strong> : <a href="http://www.myspace.com/achoopetdander" target="_blank">myspace.com/achoopetdander</a></li>\r\n		<li><strong>Temple Vibe</strong> : <a href="http://www.myspace.com/templevibe" target="_blank">myspace.com/templevibe</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style="padding-left: 30px"><a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?client=safari&amp;q=4711+12th+ave+ne+seattle&amp;oe=UTF-8&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=4711+12th+Ave+NE,+Seattle,+WA+98105&amp;gl=us&amp;ei=JG3ASqy1NJSqswPZyvBH&amp;ll=47.663552,-122.315576&amp;spn=0.007919,0.01384&amp;t=h&amp;z=16&amp;iwloc=A" target="_blank">4711 12th Ave NE <br />\r\n Seattle, WA 98105</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bring money for touring bands. Food eating commences at 7PM, Show ought to begin around 8PM.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Love,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Kenneth-</p>', 'New Crompton Potluck (09/28)', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'new-crompton-potluck-0928', '', '', '2009-09-28 00:46:11', '2009-09-28 08:46:11', '', 0, 'http://www.seattlediy.com/?p=521', 0, 'post', '', 0),
