(528, 225, '2009-10-01 09:36:08', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '<p>Hi all! I just moved to Seattle (everett actually) to intern on a goat farm. The farm is St. Johns Creamery not sure if ya''ll know it. Anyway, at home I knew where FNB met and which basements to go and see shows. Here in Seattle, I have no clue!! I wanna make some friends, see shows, get involved with some projects/movements, etc.. I''m not really sure how to do it. I"m also a little shy/nervous/feel really stupid posting this. Anyone want to give me the lowdown??? Maybe we could even meet up!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-RSB</p>', 'Philly2Seattle (I need the lowdown &amp; I need friends!)', 0, '', 'pending', 'open', 'open', '', '', '', '', '2009-10-01 09:36:08', '2009-10-01 17:36:08', '', 0, 'http://www.seattlediy.com/?p=528', 0, 'post', '', 0),
