(530, 99, '2009-10-11 22:43:09', '2009-10-12 06:43:09', 'Yes!  Check out our <a href="http://www.seattleanarchist.org/?page_id=51">list of projects tabling</a> and <a href="http://www.seattleanarchist.org/?page_id=62">our workshop/panel list and schedule</a>!  Also be sure to <a href="http://www.seattleanarchist.org/?page_id=90">read our policies</a> and <a href="http://www.seattleanarchist.org/?page_id=87">accessibility statement.</a> Use our <a href="http://www.seattleanarchist.org/?page_id=81">housing/ride board </a>to give or receive some help.  But most importantly, <strong>come to the first annual Seattle Anarchist Bookfair!</strong>\r\n\r\nMemorize this location and timing information:\r\n\r\n<strong></strong>\r\n<h2>Underground Events Center</h2>\r\n<h3>2407 1st Ave\r\n(between Battery St &amp; Wall St)\r\nSeattle, WA 98121</h3>\r\n<h2>Saturday 17th: 10 AM - 6 PM</h2>\r\n<h2>Sunday 18th: 11 AM - 6:30 PM</h2>\r\n<h3>Free and All Ages</h3>\r\nAlso, please get in touch if you would like Spanish interpretation for any particular workshops, or if you can provide any kind of intepretation, or for any other reason: seattleanarchistbookfair at riseup.net\r\n\r\n<strong>If you are tabling at the bookfair, expect an e-mail very soon explaining details such a set-up times and more!</strong>', 'THE SEATTLE ANARCHIST BOOKFAIR IS THIS WEEKEND', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'the-seattle-anarchist-bookfair-is-this-weekend', '', '\nhttp://www.seattleanarchist.org/?page_id=51', '2009-10-11 22:43:09', '2009-10-12 06:43:09', '', 0, 'http://www.seattlediy.com/?p=530', 0, 'post', '', 0);
