(533, 98, '2009-10-12 01:11:09', '2009-10-12 09:11:09', '<p style="text-align: center"><img class="aligncenter" src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2653/4004442944_347f937910.jpg" alt="Food Not Bombs Benefit Show at Healthy Times Fun Club" width="400" height="500" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>What''s your favorite freeform food movement? If you said "the Panama Canal", go to school. I mean- literally- go get an education because that made no sense...</p>\r\n\r\n<p>... Oh, you were indulging in a non sequitur. We''re cool.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This <strong>Saturday</strong> (<strong>October 17th</strong>) there will be a <strong>Food Not Bombs benefit</strong> occurring at <a href="http://www.myspace.com/healthytimesfunclub" target="_blank"><strong>Healthy Times Fun Club</strong></a>. The money will help the FNB out with costs like... Buying food! Other than that, the more important aspect of this benefit show is to inform others of FNB and all the great work the people involved with it do. It also may lead you to perhaps volunteer your time to Food Not Bombs. I''d say that would definitely be a great idea!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>There will be four acts performing that night:</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n		<li>Team Awesome! (San Diego) - <a href="http://www.myspace.com/weareteamawesome" target="_blank">myspace.com/weareteamawesome</a></li>\r\n		<li>The Taxpayers (PDX) - <a href="http://www.myspace.com/thetaxpayers" target="_blank">myspace.com/thetaxpayers</a></li>\r\n		<li>Premise Beach (Tacoma) - <a href="http://www.myspace.com/premisebeach" target="_blank">myspace.com/premisebeach</a></li>\r\n		<li>My Parade (Seattle)</li>\r\n		<li>Sky Larkin (England) - <a href="http://www.myspace.com/skylarkinskylarkin" target="_blank">myspace.com/skylarkinskylarkin</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Some things that should be known about this show is not only is it a benefit but also the last show that Premise Beach will play. The two members of that band will be moving to separate parts of the east coast. Sky Larkin are from England. That''s <a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?client=safari&amp;q=LEEDS+LS6++United+Kingdom&amp;oe=UTF-8&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hl=en&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Leeds+LS6,+United+Kingdom&amp;ll=53.704836,-1.485901&amp;spn=0.894212,2.172546&amp;z=9" target="_blank"><strong>here</strong></a>. I think we should show them how awesome Seattle is and how amazing it is that they decided to play in our fair city.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The lineup for this show is great because they''re not all local acts. Come, let''s have fun, and eat food. Oh, did I mention that Food Not Bombs will be serving food for us?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It''ll be great!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Love,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Kenneth-</p>', 'Food Not Bombs Benefit Show', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'food-not-bombs-benefit-show', '', '', '2009-10-14 14:08:39', '2009-10-14 22:08:39', '', 0, 'http://www.seattlediy.com/?p=533', 0, 'post', '', 0),
