(621, 10, '2010-01-09 08:29:10', '2010-01-09 16:29:10', '<p><img class="alignleft" src="http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4045/4259066189_c2fd6ebfbc_m.jpg" alt="Flyer" width="356" height="449" /><br class="spacer_" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><br class="spacer_" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><br class="spacer_" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><br class="spacer_" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><br class="spacer_" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><br class="spacer_" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><br class="spacer_" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><br class="spacer_" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><br class="spacer_" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><br class="spacer_" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><br class="spacer_" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><br class="spacer_" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><br class="spacer_" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><br class="spacer_" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><br class="spacer_" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ever see a place of business morph into a DIY, all ages showspace?  It''s a beautiful transformation.  Coffee shops and pizza joints just move their tables a bit to make room.   At 2020 Cycles they move completed bicycles, racks of parts, tools and machinery out of the way and the display window suddenly becomes a performance stage.  Voila, DIY all ages venue!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Unfortunately, Grass Widow had to cancel due to dire circumstances.  However, the lineup is still solid.  Broken Water from Olympia brings their wall of sound to haunt your soul.  Hornet Leg''s (also from Olympia) minimalist garage blues is just what the doctor ordered.  Local band, Witches of... will make you wish you were still a Riot Grrl in 1992.  My Parade (also local) will bring their all POC dance punk party making you want to test out your new dance moves you''ve been doing in the mirror.  Don''t miss it.</p>', 'Broken Water, Hornet Leg, Witches of..., My Parade at 2020 Cycles', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'broken-water-hornet-leg-witches-of-my-parade-at-2020-cycles', '', '', '2010-01-09 08:33:26', '2010-01-09 16:33:26', '', 0, 'http://www.seattlediy.com/?p=621', 0, 'post', '', 1),
