(673, 98, '2010-01-20 19:58:22', '2010-01-21 03:58:22', 'Here''s a really important message from Matt "Comma" Fu:\r\n<blockquote><em>...so we just had a wonderful roommate move on to the Sherwood collective and now we are looking for someone to fill her space on Feb 1st. We are a DIY venue and event space in the U-Disrict, looking forward to a bountiful\r\nspring filled with new ideas for the house including a music and lit library, workshops and classes, gardens and more! New Crompton is on 47th and 12th and you would be moving into the biggest room in this big\r\nspacious house! Or lease goes till middle of the summer. We are all fun-loving and easy going and excited for the spring and summer months of productivity! Rent is about average for the u-district and will depend on how much space and storage you want.</em>\r\n\r\n<em>shoot me an email [</em><a href="mailto:masa(at)resist.ca"><em>masa@resist.ca</em></a><em>] if you are interested! or text me on my phone (calling doesnt work so well): xxx.xxx.xxxx</em>\r\n\r\n<em>love comma\r\nmatt fu</em></blockquote>\r\nIt''s a house full of really good hearted people, for good hearted people.\r\n\r\n[caption id="" align="aligncenter" width="500" caption="A New Crompton BBQ of Spring 2009"]<a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/thekennethfoundation/3628514200/"><img title="A New Crompton BBQ of Spring 2009" src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2436/3628514200_4445dbffdf.jpg" alt="BBQ" width="500" height="375" /></a>[/caption]\r\n\r\nYeah!\r\n\r\n-Kenneth-', 'New Crompton Needs a Roommate', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'new-crompton-needs-a-roommate', '', '', '2010-01-22 00:36:21', '2010-01-22 08:36:21', '', 0, 'http://www.seattlediy.com/?p=673', 0, 'post', '', 0),
