(678, 280, '2010-01-21 16:34:26', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'Uncle Frank''s wild gay winter lodge, a queer punk shared living house in the central district is seeking a temporary subletter for february and possibly march.\r\nWe are (currently) female identified queer folks who love gardening, playing music, drinking whiskey, two-stepping, watching movies and preparing large sumptuous meals together.\r\nOur ideal match would be someone who identifies with, or is an awesome ally to the queer/ genderqueer/ trans communities that we''re a part of. Also, being small living quarters, we desire a roomie who can help keep it somewhat tidy, because it can get out of control real fast. We have two cats, a bunch of vegetable gardens, about ten cast-iron skillets, and often one or two house-guests. Interested? Come over for dinner and drinks and see if we''re a good match.\r\nxoxo!\r\n\r\nContact Nein-\r\n\r\nneinfrankenstein@yahoo.com', 'Uncle Franks Wild Gay Winter Lodge seeks sublet', 0, '', 'pending', 'open', 'open', '', '', '', '', '2010-01-21 16:34:26', '2010-01-22 00:34:26', '', 0, 'http://www.seattlediy.com/?p=678', 0, 'post', '', 0),
