(693, 98, '2010-01-27 16:50:30', '2010-01-28 00:50:30', '<object classid="clsid:d27cdb6e-ae6d-11cf-96b8-444553540000" width="400" height="300" codebase="http://download.macromedia.com/pub/shockwave/cabs/flash/swflash.cab#version=6,0,40,0"><param name="data" value="http://www.flickr.com/apps/video/stewart.swf?v=71377" /><param name="flashvars" value="intl_lang=en-us&amp;photo_secret=6c8883bdde&amp;photo_id=4140593504" /><param name="bgcolor" value="#000000" /><param name="allowFullScreen" value="true" /><param name="src" value="http://www.flickr.com/apps/video/stewart.swf?v=71377" /><param name="allowfullscreen" value="true" /><embed type="application/x-shockwave-flash" width="400" height="300" src="http://www.flickr.com/apps/video/stewart.swf?v=71377" allowfullscreen="true" bgcolor="#000000" flashvars="intl_lang=en-us&amp;photo_secret=6c8883bdde&amp;photo_id=4140593504" data="http://www.flickr.com/apps/video/stewart.swf?v=71377"></embed></object>\r\n\r\nThis <strong>Sunday</strong> (January 31st) is <strong>Get Hella Baked with Quality Papers</strong>- one of your local <em>arts &amp; crafts &amp; baking groups</em>. This weeks will be special since there will also be a <a href="http://www.hollowearthradio.org/" target="_blank">Hollow Earth Radio</a> work party in the garage as we prepare for Magma Fest 2010. If you want to get involved with Hollow Earth, this is a good and very helpful way to do it.\r\n\r\nWe will also be chasing Erin around the house (see video above). We''ll be gettin'' our craft-on, maybe bakin'' a cinna-bon ''til the lowering of the dawn... Well, not really the dawn thing. It''ll be from <strong>12:00PM - 12:00AM</strong> like the last few times. You can show up whenever and we can stay up super late.\r\n\r\nBring art supplies if you can, a list of people to write letters to, recipes of delicious things you want to make.\r\n\r\nVegan pierogi group dinner?\r\n\r\n<strong>Pet Seminary\r\n4531 5th Ave NE\r\nSeattle, WA 98105</strong>\r\n\r\ne-mail me if you have any questions: <a href="mailto:thekennethfoundation@gmail.com"><em>thekennethfoundation@gmail.com</em></a>\r\n\r\nLove,\r\n\r\n-Kenneth-', 'Arts & Crafts & Baking & Work Party', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'arts-crafts-baking-work-party', '', '', '2010-01-27 16:50:30', '2010-01-28 00:50:30', '', 0, 'http://www.seattlediy.com/?p=693', 0, 'post', '', 1),
