(781, 99, '2010-03-17 22:54:54', '2010-03-18 06:54:54', 'We''ve recorded an album\r\n&amp; now we''re working on the 2nd disc/cassette/platter.\r\nIt will be a choir singing the album in its entirety (a cappella).\r\n\r\n<img alt="" src="http://www.su-spectator.com/polopoly_fs/1.1122931!/image/3704708926.jpg" class="alignnone" width="400" />\r\n\r\nSo far 24 people have volunteered, but I''d really like to have at least 40.\r\n\r\nAnyone who can hold a tune is very welcome to join us!\r\nIt would be really nice if you have experience singing in choirs\r\nand/or are a little familiar with reading music,\r\nbut that''s not necessary!\r\nI''d like to start rehearsals in the next week or so.\r\n\r\nYou can listen to a few of our songs at\r\nwww.sonicbids.com/worldhistory\r\nto get an idea of what we do.\r\n\r\nWRITE ME! \r\nworldhistory@riseup.net', 'W e - n e e d - s i n g e r s - !', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'w-e-n-e-e-d-s-i-n-g-e-r-s', '', '', '2010-03-17 22:54:54', '2010-03-18 06:54:54', '', 0, 'http://www.seattlediy.com/?p=781', 0, 'post', '', 0),
