(905, 1, '2010-04-21 10:47:13', '2010-04-21 18:47:13', 'Check out this great event going on up at the Lakeside Collective, up in Lake City, right off the Burke-Gilman trail!\r\nIt''s on Friday, April 23rd, at 7:30pm.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.trannyroadshow.com/"><img src="http://www.trannyroadshow.com/logos/rdshwLogo.jpg" alt="" />\r\n\r\nThe Tranny Roadshow</a> is a multimedia performance art extravaganza. It is composed of an eclectic group of artists, each one self-identified as transgender, and includes poets, rappers, filmmakers, storytellers, breakdancers, rock bands, comedians, actors, folk singers, photographers, zinesters, and more. Stationary art (i.e. photography and sculpture) is displayed, but most of the presentation is the live show, a unique variety show where the expression of gender and the expression of self are inseparable. The show is a fluid entity, changing to suit the artists and the crowd, but always it is full of intelligence, fun and humor.\r\n\r\nAlthough the Tranny Roadshow is done entirely by transpeople, it is not exclusively for transpeople. It is a raucous evening of entertainment, open and accessible to people of all backgrounds.\r\n\r\nSuggested donation: $5-10. ( No one turned away!)\r\n\r\nAll Ages\r\n\r\nDANCE PARTY to follow!\r\n\r\n**We try to make our home a safe(r) space for all by minimizing the presence of transphobia, racism, ableism, sexism, sizeism, ageism, homophobia, and other forms of oppression.**\r\n\r\nOur home is wheelchair accessible. However, our driveway is quite steep and not safe for most vehicles. We can assist down the driveway in one of our vehicles, just let us know.\r\n\r\nHere''s the facebook event page: <a href="http://www.facebook.com/home.php#!/event.php?eid=112380385457288">http://www.facebook.com/home.php#!/event.php?eid=112380385457288</a>\r\n\r\nThe Lakeside Collective is at 11748 Lakeside Ave NE, Seattle, WA', 'Tranny Roadshow at the Lakeside Collective!', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'tranny-roadshow-at-the-lakeside-collective', '', '', '2010-04-21 10:48:09', '2010-04-21 18:48:09', '', 0, 'http://www.seattlediy.com/?p=905', 0, 'post', '', 0),
