(927, 14, '2010-05-02 12:37:51', '2010-05-02 20:37:51', 'Hey friends,\n\nThe second meeting to debrief and discuss the march on 4/9, as well as future community organizing, is today, March 2nd, from 5 to 7pm. Meeting space is the conference room at the Vera Project, which is at the corner of Warren Ave N &amp; Republican on Seattle Center. The building is fully ADA accessible. If you need directions or get lost, call Vera at (206) 956-8372.\n\nMetro routes 1, 2, 8, 13, 15, 16, 18, 30, and 81 all stop on the west side of Seattle Center, about a block away from Vera. There are also bike racks in front of the building. \n\nSee you soon!', 'Second meeting to discuss 4/9 march is TODAY!', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'second-meeting-to-discuss-49-march-is-today', '', '', '2010-05-02 12:37:51', '2010-05-02 20:37:51', '', 0, 'http://www.seattlediy.com/?p=927', 0, 'post', '', 0),
