(935, 14, '2010-05-05 15:56:49', '2010-05-05 23:56:49', '<img src="http://c1.ac-images.myspacecdn.com/images02/83/l_39d05c2f03cf4141971727032e083760.jpg" alt="" />\r\n\r\nDo you enjoy spontaneous cooking; throwing house shows and secret cafes; eating delicious vegan treats; Patrick Swayze and Keanu Reeves romances; playing top 40 ukulele covers; consensus-based house meetings and work parties; sunbathing on the porch; dumpster diving and living thrifty; building a vibrant, creative, welcoming and safe(r) space through living with a bunch of other rad folks?\r\n\r\nThree rooms/spaces in our gorgeous blue house in the Capitol Hill ''hood will be available by June 1st. Rent is in the 220-380 range, and utilities typically run 20-40/mo.\r\n\r\nWe''re especially looking for more queer, trans and genderqueer folks; folks of color; anti-authoritarian movers and shakers; as well as rad allies and people who are thoughtful about oppression and working on their own privilege.\r\n\r\nIf you or someone you know is interested in checking out the spaces &amp; interviewing, email parkranger [at] gmail [dot] com for more details!', 'Communal queer veg*n house seeks three new roomies!', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'communal-queer-vegn-house-seeks-three-new-roomies', '', '', '2010-05-05 15:56:49', '2010-05-05 23:56:49', '', 0, 'http://www.seattlediy.com/?p=935', 0, 'post', '', 0),
