(1003, 99, '2010-06-06 11:45:40', '2010-06-06 19:45:40', 'Tomorrow, June 7th, we will be gathering outside the Seattle Mexican Consulate (2132 3rd Ave. 98121) to show solidarity with comrades in Oaxaca who continue to be besieged by armed paramilitaries, and also to create a public awareness of the June 8th Bety Cariño and Jyri Jaakkola Humanitarian Caravan, which will attempt to break the paramilitary siege of the municipality of San Juan Copala and save the lives of  the more than 70 families who are surviving under inhuman conditions.\r\n\r\nWe seek to pressure the Mexican government to call off its paramilitary thugs, and to prevent another massacre.\r\n\r\n<strong>June 7th, Noon: </strong>Representatives from <a href="http://www.lelo.org/">LELO</a> will be speaking.\r\n<strong>June 7th, 1pm:</strong> Anarchist &amp; anti-authoritarian rally.\r\n\r\nBackground information, news &amp; updates, and a documentary on  repression and resistance in Oaxaca: <a href="http://elenemigocomun.net/">http://elenemigocomun.net/</a>\r\nA leaflet to be handed out June 7th: <a href="http://arcticcirclecollective.info/articles/24/the-fingers-of-an-iron-fist">http://arcticcirclecollective.info/articles/24/the-fingers-of-an-iron-fist</a>\r\nAn 8.5 x 11 flier promoting June 7th: <a href="http://arcticcirclecollective.info/file_download/10/oaxaca.pdf">http://arcticcirclecollective.info/file_download/10/oaxaca.pdf</a>\r\nThe original call-out: <a href="http://news.infoshop.org/article.php?story=20100601225740286">http://news.infoshop.org/article.php?story=20100601225740286</a>', 'REMINDER: June 7 Day of Solidarity with Oaxaca Tomorrow!', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'reminder-june-7-day-of-solidarity-with-oaxaca-tomorrow', '', '\nhttp://news.infoshop.org/article.php?story=20100601225740286', '2010-06-06 11:47:02', '2010-06-06 19:47:02', '', 0, 'http://www.seattlediy.com/?p=1003', 0, 'post', '', 0),
