(1016, 98, '2010-06-10 18:56:29', '2010-06-11 02:56:29', '<p style="text-align: center;"><object classid="clsid:d27cdb6e-ae6d-11cf-96b8-444553540000" width="549" height="412" codebase="http://download.macromedia.com/pub/shockwave/cabs/flash/swflash.cab#version=6,0,40,0"><param name="allowfullscreen" value="true" /><param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always" /><param name="src" value="http://vimeo.com/moogaloop.swf?clip_id=10934813&amp;server=vimeo.com&amp;show_title=1&amp;show_byline=1&amp;show_portrait=0&amp;color=59a5d1&amp;fullscreen=1" /><embed type="application/x-shockwave-flash" width="549" height="412" src="http://vimeo.com/moogaloop.swf?clip_id=10934813&amp;server=vimeo.com&amp;show_title=1&amp;show_byline=1&amp;show_portrait=0&amp;color=59a5d1&amp;fullscreen=1" allowscriptaccess="always" allowfullscreen="true"></embed></object>\r\n<em></em>\r\n\r\n<em>Well...</em> you ought to be\r\n\r\nAfter returning from a brief trip and realizing that I''m behind on updating my schedule book, I decided to take some time to update it. After proceeding with <em>The Scheduling (the major motion picture)</em>, I have found that <strong>there are a million events happening tomorrow</strong> (Friday 6.10.2010 (m/dd/yyyy))!\r\n\r\nHere''s a brief list of yr options.\r\n\r\n<strong>Cairo Gallery</strong> (<em>507 e. mercer</em>); <strong>8 - 11 pm</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Gun Outfit</li>\r\n	<li>Milk Music</li>\r\n	<li>Nice Smile</li>\r\n	<li>Eel Eater</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Pet Seminary</strong> (<em>4531 5th ave ne</em>); <strong>6 - 9 pm</strong>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.seattlediy.com/?p=1007" target="_blank">http://www.seattlediy.com/?p=1007</a>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Grr</li>\r\n	<li>Fishboy</li>\r\n	<li>Madeline Ava</li>\r\n	<li>Max Weis, and Mitch</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Hollow Earth House</strong> (4054  latona ave ne) <strong>8 - 11:30 pm</strong>\r\n\r\nFilm Screenings by...\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Eric Ostrowski</li>\r\n	<li>So Spun We Spun West</li>\r\n	<li>Jean Smith</li>\r\n	<li>David Lester</li>\r\n	<li>Clyde Petersen</li>\r\n	<li>Spencer Williams</li>\r\n	<li>...and maybe more!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nMusical Performance by...\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Horde of Two (contains 1 David of <a href="http://www.krecs.com/html/artists/artistpagetest.php?interest=23" target="_blank">Mecca Normal</a>)</li>\r\n	<li>Lori Goldston (amazing)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Healthy Times Fun Club</strong> (you know)<strong> 8 - 12 pm</strong>\r\n<blockquote><em>We''re throwing a show to raise some funds to get folks from Seattle to participant in two events happening in Detroit this summer. The first is the Allied Media Conference (AMC), a conference for media-based orgs and folks fighting for media-justice.\r\nThe second (just days after the AMC) is the big one, the US Social Forum, a radical movement building process that will be gatehring around over 20,000 activists from across the country.</em></blockquote>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>My Parade</li>\r\n	<li>Mutiny Mutiny</li>\r\n	<li>Cloudbustr</li>\r\n	<li>more...</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Vera Project</strong> (305 Harrison Street) <strong>7:30 - 12 pm</strong>\r\n\r\n<em>Noise for the Needy benefit show</em>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Portland Cello Project (PCP)</li>\r\n	<li>Grand Hallway</li>\r\n	<li>Angelo Spencer et les Hauts Sommets</li>\r\n	<li>Tomten</li>\r\n	<li>Drew Grow &amp; The Pastors’ Wives</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Black Lodge</strong> (I still don''t know the address) <strong>9 pm - 1 am</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Drug Purse</li>\r\n	<li>Basemint</li>\r\n	<li>Karma Vision (KS)</li>\r\n	<li>Happy Birthday Secret Weapon</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>The Josephine</strong> (65th st in Ballard) <strong>9 pm - 1 am </strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Case and Control</li>\r\n	<li>By Sunlight</li>\r\n	<li>Snowman Plan</li>\r\n	<li>Austenitic</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nDo what you can, feel what you want- maybe stay inside if inclined. Cuddle or something. <a href="http://www.seattlediy.com/?p=1007">Why not come to Pet Seminary</a> before heading off to anything else happening in town, hang out with the Pet Seminarians and their <strong>Dogciples</strong>. Maybe do some<strong> Tofu Tithing</strong>.\r\n\r\nAnything else you can think of?\r\n\r\neh?\r\n\r\nEH?', 'Friday? Confused?(!)', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'friday-im-confused', '', 'http://www.seattlediy.com/?p=1007\nhttp://www.seattlediy.com/?p=1007\nhttp://www.seattlediy.com/?p=1007', '2010-06-11 12:33:31', '2010-06-11 20:33:31', '', 0, 'http://www.seattlediy.com/?p=1016', 0, 'post', '', 0),
