(1143, 172, '2010-07-31 15:21:53', '2010-07-31 23:21:53', 'Out of the flaming wreck of the Ruckus collective, a new (and much more sexy) journal is emerging! This project is in its early stages and while some content has been gathered, much more is needed to fill this beauty out. ALL art/fiction/non-fiction/poetry/polemic is HIGHLY lusted after. We of this new project (tentatively entitled <em>ENNUI</em>) are more thorough and generally more dedicated than we were when Ruckus still was existent, meaning the end product will be some BOMB-ASS SHIT. We envision a magazine that strikes a balance - we sharpen our knives while still avoiding excess political dogma (we have a very low tolerance for activism), we promote the sexiness of our friends'' forays and adventures, we think intellectual property doesn''t roll easily off the tongue. This will be a quarterly publication at best, so submit while it''s hot! Yer hot!\r\n\r\nContact//Submit images and text to: thesedarkwings@riseup.net\r\n\r\nLet''s get famous and buy diamond grillz. Srsly.\r\n\r\nArtio', 'New! Seattle Journal! Submit!', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'new-seattle-journal-submit', '', '', '2010-07-31 15:21:53', '2010-07-31 23:21:53', '', 0, 'http://www.seattlediy.com/?p=1143', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(1139, 305, '2010-07-22 08:58:18', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'The Office of Dr Glorious is looking for a lovely new roommate!  We are a Central District house with four bedrooms, typically housing four people.  The room you would be living in is a large forest green dwelling with high ceilings and three windows.  We have a basement space suitable for musical projects, art projects and anything else you think you may want to use it for.   We have some quiet house shows from time to time as well.  The three roommates that are staying are in their mid twenties and early thirties and all work with children.  All you really need in order to fit in here is the ability to wash a few dishes now and then and generally be a friendly, open, un-turdlike human.   Ideally looking for a female-ish person to take the room in order to keep things balanced but any and all who apply will be considered.  As noted in the title this room is available anywhere between the 1st and 15th of August, utilities are not included in the rent price but tend to stay low, usually the put the rent for the place up to a whopping $360 a month.\r\n\r\nPlease call or email to set up a time to view the room, and meet and greet the roommates.\r\n\r\nBest Wishes,\r\n\r\nAmanda\r\n\r\n360 888 9514', 'The Office of Dr Glorious-gem of the Central District-Seeks a new roommate $310', 0, 'yay!  I love this house!', 'draft', 'open', 'open', '', '', '', '', '2010-07-22 08:58:18', '2010-07-22 16:58:18', '', 0, 'http://www.seattlediy.com/?p=1139', 0, 'post', '', 0),
