(1063, 201, '2010-06-25 21:02:14', '2010-06-26 05:02:14', '<img alt="" src="http://www.healthyvending.com/img/sliders/no_money.jpg" title="no money" class="aligncenter" width="300" height="278" />\n\nIs your freebox overflowing with recently unburied treasure? Are you doing your spring cleaning and have some weird/wonderful things you need to get off your hands? Are you in desperate need of some totally free clothes, movies, books, CDs, household goods, instruments, etc etc?\n\nJust as I suspected!\n\nWell, the Really Really Free Market (aka the answer to all your prayers) is really really happening today!\n\nthe details:\n\nCome join us at Pratt Park (on 20th between Yesler and Jackson in the Central Area)! RRFM organizers will be there from noon to 4pm, but really it all depends on YOUR participation.\n\nThis is how it works: bring your freebox! Clothes, movies, music, house goods, snacks, shoes, whatever else that you no longer need and think someone might be able to use. Why buy new things when there is so much extra stuff just floating around our community? Everything is totally free, bring what you don’t want anymore, take away new finds. At the end of the day someone will scoop up everything left over and take it down to be donated to Lifelong AIDS Alliance.\n\nIt’s like the biggest free box of your dreams! Look for us tomorrow, you’ll see picnic tables covered with stuff (or if it’s raining, look for us under the covered area.\n\nSee you there!', 'really really free market tomorrow (saturday)!', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'really-really-free-market-tomorrow-saturday', '', '', '2010-06-25 21:02:14', '2010-06-26 05:02:14', '', 0, 'http://www.seattlediy.com/?p=1063', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(1095, 98, '2010-07-05 11:46:21', '2010-07-05 19:46:21', '<img class="aligncenter" src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2527/3774798996_1f7b11cd96.jpg" alt="" width="500" height="375" />\r\n\r\nToday at Golden Gardens park (8498 seaview pl NW) there will be a beach show from 5:30 - 9:00 . Here''s the event description via Shelby Turner.\r\n<blockquote>summer time beach show, first in a series of a million\r\n\r\ngreg mullen and lindsay clark are on tour, they''re going to play a handful of songs each\r\n\r\namidst that, expect a song or two from:\r\n\r\nmegabog\r\nsundance kids\r\niji\r\nmammary\r\nslashed tires\r\ncumulus\r\nla llorona\r\n\r\nand, if YOU want to play a song or two, you should...!\r\n\r\nwe''ll get there early and pick a little spot on the beach. we''ll put up a little sign to point you in the right direction. we''ll pass a hat around to support our touring buddies. sounds fun?</blockquote>\r\nWhen that gets done, everyone can head over to the Black Lodge for a megamazing show featuring Chain And The Gang, Basemint, Night Beats, and Neighbors.\r\n\r\n<em>Yeah yeah</em>.', 'Beach Show Yeah Yeah (today)', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'beach-show-yeah-yeah-today', '', '', '2010-07-05 11:46:21', '2010-07-05 19:46:21', '', 0, 'http://www.seattlediy.com/?p=1095', 0, 'post', '', 1),
