(1108, 98, '2010-07-10 14:28:01', '2010-07-10 22:28:01', '<div id="_mcePaste"><img class="aligncenter" src="http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4005/4667752087_87e57cb5a0.jpg" alt="" width="500" height="375" />Choose yr destiny (or something like that)</div>\r\n<div><strong>Greenhouse - 8pm / doors at 9pm</strong></div>\r\n<div><em>A K Records Pre-What the Heck Fest Hootenanny/Send-off!</em> - Which is weird, because only half of the bands playing are K bands. Right, right?</div>\r\n<div id="_mcePaste">\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Calvin Johnson</li>\r\n	<li>Karl Blau</li>\r\n	<li>Your Heart Breaks</li>\r\n	<li>Cumulus</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="_mcePaste"><strong>Healthy Times Fun Club - 8pm</strong></div>\r\n<div><em>This is TOTALLY a benefit show- help benefit.</em></div>\r\n<div id="_mcePaste">\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Thousands</li>\r\n	<li>Wet Paint</li>\r\n	<li>Summer Blondes</li>\r\n	<li>Naomi Punk</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="_mcePaste"><strong>Black Lodge - 9pm</strong></div>\r\n<div id="_mcePaste">\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Kid Crash (PDX)</li>\r\n	<li>Native</li>\r\n	<li>My Heart To Joy (CT)</li>\r\n	<li>Livingston Seagull</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>', 'Fun Tonight (friday)', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'events-tonight-friday', '', '', '2010-07-10 16:47:12', '2010-07-11 00:47:12', '', 0, 'http://www.seattlediy.com/?p=1108', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(1081, 98, '2010-07-03 10:51:12', '2010-07-03 18:51:12', '<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter" title="Clyde Benefit" src="http://www.ourheartsbreak.com/images/final.png" alt="" width="440" height="570" /></p>\r\nI case you cats haven''t heard, our beloved badass friend, Clyde Petersen was burglarized two weeks ago and all of his $4,500 in essential filmmaking gear was stolen. Clyde doesn''t have a real job and he gets by through making documentaries and music videos from his own film production business, <a href="http://doitforthegirls.com/" target="_blank">Do It for the Girls</a>, and from the occasional tour managing / band management gigs.\r\n\r\nSo... <strong>TONIGHT</strong>! at <strong>20/20 Cycle</strong> (<a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?client=safari&amp;oe=UTF-8&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;q=2020+e+union&amp;fb=1&amp;gl=us&amp;hnear=&amp;cid=0,0,831484307808316122&amp;ei=IYIvTPTqNoPSsAOrtKXgBQ&amp;ved=0CBMQnwIwAA&amp;hq=2020+e+union&amp;t=h&amp;z=16&amp;iwloc=A" target="_blank">2020 E. Union</a>) at <strong>8pm sharp</strong>, this mega-benefit will occur. This was put together the day after the burglary by <a href="http://www.hollowearthradio.org/programs/27">Garrett</a>, <a href="http://www.hollowearthradio.org/programs/31">Amber</a> and <a href="http://www.hollowearthradio.org/programs/56">Forrest</a> and we''ve all pitched in since to help Clyde with whatever equipment and gear he needs / needed to finish his badass documentary <em>The Unspeakable</em> (it''s really good: covers some NW artists). Any monetary help that you (the reader) can provide is <em>totally cool</em> and more info is here at <a href="http://www.ourheartsbreak.com/">ourheartsbreak.com</a>.\r\n\r\nHere''s the line-up:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size: 13.3333px;">Vicky Galinsky</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size: 13.3333px;">Spencer Sult (Generifus)</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size: 13.3333px;">Low Hums</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size: 13.3333px;">Lori Goldston</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size: 13.3333px;">Ian Ostrowski</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size: 13.3333px;">Blanket Truth</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size: 13.3333px;">Slashed Tires</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size: 13.3333px;">Kimya Dawson</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size: 13.3333px;">LAKE</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size: 13.3333px;">Pica Beats</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size: 13.3333px;">Matt Fu (1985)</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size: 13.3333px;">Stebmo</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size: 13.3333px;">Triumph of Lethargy</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAnd a video that Clyde has made:\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><object classid="clsid:d27cdb6e-ae6d-11cf-96b8-444553540000" width="480" height="385" codebase="http://download.macromedia.com/pub/shockwave/cabs/flash/swflash.cab#version=6,0,40,0"><param name="allowFullScreen" value="true" /><param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always" /><param name="src" value="http://www.youtube.com/v/KVmJbv3oUy8&amp;hl=en_US&amp;fs=1" /><param name="allowfullscreen" value="true" /><embed type="application/x-shockwave-flash" width="480" height="385" src="http://www.youtube.com/v/KVmJbv3oUy8&amp;hl=en_US&amp;fs=1" allowscriptaccess="always" allowfullscreen="true"></embed></object>', 'Benefit for Clyde Petersen (tonight!)', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'benefit-for-clyde-petersen-tonight', '', '', '2010-07-03 10:59:32', '2010-07-03 18:59:32', '', 0, 'http://www.seattlediy.com/?p=1081', 0, 'post', '', 0),
