(1128, 98, '2010-07-20 20:21:40', '2010-07-21 04:21:40', '<img class="aligncenter" src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2454/3902449523_19aa729c12.jpg" alt="" width="444" height="500" />Killer cool.\r\n\r\nLast years'' Carousel Fest was great. It was great because of the bands and venues both <strong>mostly</strong> because we had some fucking-amazing volunteers. Take Chloe, Susanna and Mike-for example (pictured above from right to left). They were so into volunteering and having fun doing it. Just look at those fun poses!\r\n\r\n"But, Kenneth, what are you getting at, bra-dude?"\r\n\r\nWhat I''m getting at is <strong>if you''re interested in volunteering for Carousel Fest 2010, then contact me</strong> via <a href="mailto:slashedtires@gmail.com" target="_blank"><strong>slashedtires@gmail.com</strong></a>. This year Carousel Fest will be taking place from <strong>August 27th to the 29th</strong>.\r\n\r\nWe''re so excited about this.\r\n\r\nLike, totally.\r\n\r\n(<a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/thekennethfoundation/sets/72157622317770764/">here are some photos from last year</a>)', 'Carousel Fest 2010 Needs YOU!', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'carousel-fest-2010-needs-you', '', '', '2010-07-20 20:27:36', '2010-07-21 04:27:36', '', 0, 'http://www.seattlediy.com/?p=1128', 0, 'post', '', 0),
