(1144, 172, '2010-07-29 20:40:01', '2010-07-30 04:40:01', 'Out of the flaming wreck of the Ruckus collective, a new (and much more sexy) journal is emerging! This project is in its early stages and while some content has been gathered, much more is needed to fill this beauty out. ALL art/fiction/non-fiction/poetry/polemic is HIGHLY lusted after. We of this new project (tentatively entitled <em>ENNUI</em>) are more thorough and generally more dedicated than we were when Ruckus still was existent, meaning the end product will be some BOMB-ASS SHIT. We envision a magazine that strikes a balance - we sharpen our knives while still avoiding excess political dogma (we have a very low tolerance for activism), we promote the sexiness of our friends'' forays and adventures, we think intellectual property doesn''t roll easily off the tongue. This will be a quarterly publication at best, so submit while it''s hot! Yer hot!\n\nContact//Submit images and text to: thesedarkwings@riseup.net\n\nLet''s get famous and buy diamond grillz. Srsly.', 'New! Seattle Journal! Submit!', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1143-revision', '', '', '2010-07-29 20:40:01', '2010-07-30 04:40:01', '', 1143, 'http://www.seattlediy.com/?p=1144', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
