(1198, 3, '2010-08-11 00:41:20', '2010-08-11 08:41:20', '<a href="http://www.seattlediy.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/06/bookfair_web.jpg"><img src="http://www.seattlediy.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/06/bookfair_web-220x300.jpg" alt="" width="220" height="300" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1072" /></a>\r\nthe second annual <a href="http://www.seattleanarchist.org">seattle anarchist book fair</a> is less than two weeks away, and a truly excellent mass of northwest radicals will descend upon the vera project.\r\n\r\nwhile the tables &amp; workshop slots are full, the book fair is still OUR space. you don''t need an invitation, but we''d like to give a gentle nudge and maybe a wink at yr capture the black flag, guerilla workshop, double-dutch, marching band, poetry reading, film screening, dance party.... this is yr call-out! the possibilities are endless!\r\n\r\nand if you''d like a more traditional way to participate, there are many volunteers needed to pull off a full weekend of radical fun. <a href="mailto:info@seattleanarchist.org">email</a> or stop by left bank books to sign up.', 'seattle anarchist book fair - a call out! ', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1179-autosave', '', '', '2010-08-11 00:41:20', '2010-08-11 08:41:20', '', 1179, 'http://www.seattlediy.com/?p=1198', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1151, 3, '2010-08-03 13:28:43', '2010-08-03 21:28:43', 'this sunday, august 8th, at the arctic circle: a showing of BORN IN FLAMES to support the seattle anarchist bookfair! 7pm snacktime, 8pm movie. bring a few dollars for the bookfair.\r\n\r\n<img src="http://www.seattlediy.com/wp-admin/admin-ajax.php?action=imgedit-preview&amp;_ajax_nonce=5e2c40740e&amp;postid=1162&amp;rand=8552">\r\n\r\nBORN IN FLAMES takes place 10 years after a socialist revolution in the united states, where women are still struggling for jobs, health care, safety and autonomy. through the women''s army and other radical groups, they begin to fight back. the growth and impact of the women''s army is tracked by the socialist women''s media and the feds, leading to the kidnapping of a prominent member. when she dies in prison, the splintered groups organize together and attack. meeeow!\r\n<code>\r\n</code>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.cineasten.de/filme/born-in-flames,trailer.html">born in flames - trailer</a>', 'BORN IN FLAMES: film screening 8/8', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'born-in-flames-film-screening-88', '', '', '2010-08-03 15:32:20', '2010-08-03 23:32:20', '', 0, 'http://www.seattlediy.com/?p=1151', 0, 'post', '', 0),
