(1181, 3, '2010-08-04 23:29:46', '2010-08-05 07:29:46', '<img alt="" src="http://t0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRodWs9QTgZLyS155VkimvQ0gJUPcmo1WyofD9U6U7SonSjlyM&amp;t=1&amp;usg=__rTtJ4BTiI-fFEE3EL6Uomth2s2w=" class="aligncenter" width="201" height="251" />\n\nWhat are you doing this weekend? Why, <a href="http://www.rosecitycopwatch.wordpress.com">Rose City Cop Watch</a> (Portland) are coming up this Saturday, August 7th, for a training!\n\n    * 12pm Potluck Lunch will be to discuss the issues and needs in our communities for why we need police accountability and Cop Watch\n    * 1pm 2 hrs Security Culture Training\n    * 3pm break\n    * 3:30pm 2 hrs Know Your Rights &amp; Cop Watch Training \n\n\nCasa Latina\n17th &amp; Jackson\n317 17th Ave S, Seattle, Wa 98144\n\n#14 to 16th Ave, uphill from # 7 Rainier Ave, #60/36 12th &amp; Jackson, or downhill from # 8/48 on 23rd &amp; Jackson', 'Copwatch &amp; security culture training w/ the Rose City Copwatch!', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1153-revision-3', '', '', '2010-08-04 23:29:46', '2010-08-05 07:29:46', '', 1153, 'http://www.seattlediy.com/?p=1181', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1179, 3, '2010-08-11 00:40:11', '2010-08-11 08:40:11', '<a href="http://www.seattleanarchist.org"><img src="http://lh6.ggpht.com/_4CkMTIcoDbo/TCvtBc1J_9I/AAAAAAAAAU0/pGAUJVHaTDY/bookfair_web.jpg" alt="" width="220" height="300" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1072" /></a>\r\nthe second annual <a href="http://www.seattleanarchist.org">seattle anarchist book fair</a> is less than two weeks away, and a truly excellent mass of northwest radicals will descend upon the vera project.\r\n\r\nwhile the tables &amp; workshop slots are full, the book fair is still OUR space. you don''t need an invitation, but we''d like to give a gentle nudge and maybe a wink at yr capture the black flag, guerilla workshop, double-dutch, marching band, poetry reading, film screening, dance party.... this is yr call-out! the possibilities are endless!\r\n\r\nand if you''d like a more traditional way to participate, there are many volunteers needed to pull off a full weekend of radical fun. <a href="mailto:info@seattleanarchist.org">email</a> or stop by left bank books to sign up.', 'seattle anarchist book fair - a call out! ', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'seattle-anarchist-book-fair-a-call-out', '', '', '2010-08-11 00:44:10', '2010-08-11 08:44:10', '', 0, 'http://www.seattlediy.com/?p=1179', 0, 'post', '', 0),
