(1230, 3, '2010-08-24 10:54:07', '2010-08-24 18:54:07', '<p align="center"><img src="http://www.lasthours.org.uk/wp-content/uploads/2009/11/zines-on-toast-tour-72dpi.jpg"></p>\n\nJust one week after the Seattle Anarchist Book Fair, some UK <a href="http://www.lasthours.org.uk/">anarcha-zinesters</a> are hitting the road with Alex Wrekk (PDX Zine Symposium, Stolen Sharpie Revolution)!\n\n<p align="center">Tuesday, August 31 | 7-9pm\n$3-5 donation, sliding scale\nzinesontoast.org</p>\n \nThey will discuss UK zine culture and tell stories from Alex''s trip to the UK last year, plus tales of the London zine symposium, vegan mass catering, failing to punch Tony Blair in the face, UK social centres, revolution, punk rock, anarchy and more!', 'Zines on Toast Tour hits the ZAPP', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'zines-on-toast-tour-hits-the-zapp', '', '', '2010-08-24 10:54:07', '2010-08-24 18:54:07', '', 0, 'http://www.seattlediy.com/?p=1230', 0, 'post', '', 0),
