(1255, 99, '2010-08-31 17:14:52', '2010-09-01 01:14:52', 'you may have heard about the brutal murders that happened yesterday and today by police in washington state (<a href="http://arcticcirclecollective.info/articles/51/seattle-cops-kill-again">Seattle Cops Kill Again</a>). with all of the work being done to quell anti-cop sentiment, a quick response to this news is appropriate.\r\n\r\nfolks will gather for literature distribution regarding these two specific murders this FRIDAY 9/3 from NOON to 2 pm in front of seattle central community college, on the corner of broadway and pine. people are encouraged to make banners, signs, their own handouts/pamphlets, and respect a diversity of tactics regarding people''s public response to these tragedies.\r\n\r\nthis is a perfect opportunity to continue conversations regarding strategies for further timely community or individual responses to cop killings, as well as to find each other while addressing our rage at the police/state.', 'friday anti-cop demonstration', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'friday-anti-cop-demonstration', '', '', '2010-08-31 19:02:55', '2010-09-01 03:02:55', '', 0, 'http://www.seattlediy.com/?p=1255', 0, 'post', '', 0),
