(1248, 201, '2010-08-27 15:43:23', '2010-08-27 23:43:23', '<p style="text-align: center"><strong>The Really Really Free Market is here again!</strong>\r\n<img class="aligncenter" src="http://www.timeout.com/img/10018924/w450/image.jpg" alt="" width="450" height="450" /></p>\r\nCome over to <strong>Pratt Park</strong> (20th and Yesler in the Central District) <strong>between noon and 4pm</strong>. <strong>Bring what you got</strong> (clothes? shoes? furniture? books? food? anything re-usable!), and <strong>take what you want</strong>. No buying/selling/bartering. Just sharing resources and spreading the love. At 4, anything left will be donated to Lifelong AIDS Alliance.\r\n\r\n<strong>On a personal note</strong>, my house is relocating to Capitol Hill and we are getting rid of tons of clothing and other assorted goods. I can personally guarantee <strong>at least 4 boxes of quality free stuff.</strong> If you bring more, it will be like a party of freedom resulting in stylish new outfits for everyone.\r\n\r\nSee you tomorrow!<img class="aligncenter" src="http://fast.mediamatic.nl/f/sjnh/image/624/47845-334-500.jpg" alt="" width="334" height="500" />', 'Really Really Free Market TOMORROW! (Saturday 8/27)', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'really-really-free-market-tomorrow-saturday-827', '', '', '2010-08-27 15:47:02', '2010-08-27 23:47:02', '', 0, 'http://www.seattlediy.com/?p=1248', 0, 'post', '', 0),
