(1295, 98, '2010-09-10 09:05:56', '2010-09-10 17:05:56', '<em>Via Garrett Kelly</em>\r\n<blockquote><strong>Friday Sept. 10th, 2010 / 7:30pm - 11:00pm</strong>\r\n\r\nLive in the new Hollow Earth Radio space (<a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?f=d&amp;source=s_d&amp;saddr=400+Broad+Street,+Seattle,+WA+98109-4607+(Space+Needle)&amp;daddr=2018+A+East+Union+Street,+Seattle,+WA+98122+(Hollow+Earth+Radio)&amp;geocode=Fb-g1gIdGRm1-CENIROz5337OyktVsv4RRWQVDF5EDa-pIvBRw%3BFRaF1gIdIMW1-CHPxGBvwZZzOg&amp;hl=en&amp;mra=pd&amp;mrcr=0&amp;sll=47.616861,-122.327268&amp;sspn=0.040211,0.082054&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;ll=47.614727,-122.3283&amp;spn=0.040212,0.082054&amp;t=h&amp;z=14" target="_blank">2018 A East Union</a>)!\r\n\r\nOpen to the public!\r\nFree, but donations always accepted!\r\n\r\nEVENING EVENTS INCLUDE:\r\n\r\n<strong>The Wedding</strong>, 15 minute short film by Garrett Kelly. This will make you cringe. Never shown in public before.\r\n\r\n<strong>Eric Ostrowski</strong> will premiere new film "Wed Wagon". Also, film and sound performance - with 2 16mm projectors and violin.\r\n\r\n<strong>Slashed Tires</strong>, finger snapping &amp; vibrato\r\n\r\n<strong>Tom Tafejian</strong>, music scored to photography. More about that here: <a rel="nofollow" href="http://soundsfoundinpictures.tumblr.com/" target="_blank">http://soundsfoundinpictures.tumblr.com/</a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Justin Clifford Rhody</strong> - ''found'' film: Move Outs.\r\nAlso poetry performance thing: "J.R.''s poetry problem"\r\nNo idea what he''s going to do, but he never disappoints.\r\n\r\nCoffee served.\r\nSmoke your damn cigarettes somewhere else.</blockquote>', 'An Exclusive Meeting of the Hollow Earth Radio Beatniks Anonymous', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'an-exclusive-meeting-of-the-hollow-earth-radio-beatniks-anonymous', '', '', '2010-09-10 09:07:53', '2010-09-10 17:07:53', '', 0, 'http://www.seattlediy.com/?p=1295', 0, 'post', '', 0),
