(3, '<p>Thanks for checking out the new website. If there&#39;s anything that you think would make things better (aesthetically, or usefullness-wise), let us know!</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>sdiycollective at gmail dot com.</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>-Benji</p>', '2008-12-17 19:53:13', 3, 1, 2, '', '', 0, 0, 1, NULL, '67.170.107.229'),
(4, '<p><span style=\\"font-size: x-small;\\"><span id=\\"ctl00_ctl00_cpMain_cpMain_BulletinRead_ltl_body\\">a bunch of us at dancylvania are going to be selling records, clothes*, crafts, weird knick-knacks, zines, household stuff, etc, in our living. come before we go and sell shit to stores/ebay! or just come over for brunch (around 12) and hang out in front of the fire.<br style=\\"display: none;\\" /><br /><br /><br />Records! Clothes! Zines! Books! Crafts!<br /><br />Or just come and hang out and eat snacks, sit around the fire, listen to music, and do WHATEVER!<br /><br />110 Harvard Ave E<br />Seattle, WA 98102<br /><br /><a href=\\"http://www.myspace.com/dancylvaniahouse\\" target="_blank"><a href="http://www" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">http://www</a>. myspace. com/dancylvaniahouse</a></span></span></p>', '2008-12-17 19:57:19', 4, 1, 1, '', '', 0, 0, 1, NULL, '67.170.107.229'),
(5, '<p>Secret Cafe + Movie Night<br />A Benefit for Solid Ground / Community Alliance for Global Justice<br />Short movies on the topic of Food Justice</p>\r\n<p>January 3rd<br />@ Dancylvania<br />110 Harvard Ave E<br />Seattle, WA 98102</p>', '2008-12-19 14:10:07', 5, 1, 3, '', '', 0, 0, 1, NULL, '67.170.107.229'),
(6, '<p>Hey buddies,</p>\r\n<p>I want to offer up my services to teach drum lessons for beginners. I have a practice space with a drum set, and I have experience teaching beginning drum lessons at a teen center and have done a number of lessons for friends.</p>\r\n<p>I try to teach people to find their own style and not force people to drum according to how I play, but I also aim to challenge people to try to think outside of what&#39;s comfortable.</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>I&#39;m most familiar with teaching beginners. I usually ask for $20/session (this is negotiable for those with no or low-incomes, but I&#39;m broke too!), and sessions are usually around an hour.</p>\r\n<p>To see how I play drums: <a rel=\\"nofollow\\" href=\\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-lYMKadHosw\\" target="_blank">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v.....lYMKadHosw</a> or <a rel=\\"nofollow\\" href=\\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wdsHPwSoos0\\" target="_blank">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v.....dsHPwSoos0</a></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>Email me at heartxmurmur at yahoo dot com if you&#39;re interested!</p>', '2008-12-19 14:38:50', 6, 1, 1, '', '', 0, 0, 1, 'a:2:{i:0;a:2:{s:2:"by";s:5:"Benji";s:2:"at";i:1229719224;}i:1;a:2:{s:2:"by";s:5:"Benji";s:2:"at";i:1229728779;}}', '67.170.107.229'),
