(16, '<p>Hey All,</p>\r\n<p>I&#39;m looking to start a new house/find an existing house that would be a good space to:</p>\r\n<p>-Do massage(maybe more than one massage therapist to create a massage space)</p>\r\n<p>-Have shows</p>\r\n<p>-Bake beautiful vegan goodness</p>\r\n<p>-Host meetings/craft nights</p>\r\n<p>-Play music</p>\r\n<p>My current living situation is nice enough, but not in the direction I&#39;m looking to go.&nbsp; Looking for something in February/March-ish</p>\r\n<p>I&#39;m a queer hispanic female, so other qpoc people or allies would be rad.</p>\r\n<p>If your interested, please drop me a line at <a href=\\"mailto:yes.itsallpossible@gmail.com\\" target="_blank">yes.itsallpossible@gmail.com</a></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>Thanks.</p>\r\n<p>a.</p>', '2009-01-06 18:57:40', 13, 32, 1, '', '', 0, 0, 1, NULL, '96.26.192.195'),
(17, '<p>Hey Guys,</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>My name is Don, I play in a band called Action Beat, who release music on southern records - <a href=\\"http://www.southern.com\\" target="_blank">http://www.southern.com</a> - We are a 6-14 piece nosie/punk/rock band, who play with several drummers, and about 4-6 guitars. We&#39;re influenced by sonic youth, Glenn Branca, Fugazi, the ex and loads more....</p>\r\n<p>We are going to embark on our first US tour in September/October, and are looking for shows in Seattle area around the beginning of October 2009. Sure, this is a long way off, but if you are interested in booking us, please get in touch with me at <a href=\\"mailto:fortissimorecords@hotmail.com\\" target="_blank">fortissimorecords@hotmail.com</a></p>\r\n<p>Thanks,</p>\r\n<p>Don</p>\r\n<p><a href=\\"http://www.myspace.com/actionbeat\\" target="_blank">http://www.myspace.com/actionbeat</a></p>', '2009-01-08 14:27:52', 14, 31, 3, '', '', 0, 0, 1, NULL, '71.247.26.247'),
