(20, '<p>I work at a drop-in center for street involved youth and I&#39;m trying to put together an earn-a-bike program. I&#39;m seeking advice re: this.</p>\r\n<p>General idea in the past has been that youth spend 8 hours working on a bike with a volunteer (who knows what they&#39;re doing) and then ride away with a shiny new bicycle, a helmet, and a lock. However, it hasn&#39;t functioned effectively for a while. Essentially, I&#39;d like suggestions for creating a working system and also for obtaining bike parts (most of what we have is junk).</p>\r\n<p>That&#39;s the basics, I thought about writing up everything that we&#39;ve thought of already etc. etc., but that seems like too much work right now, so forgive me if I say . . . yeahhh, we tried that . . .</p>\r\n<p>Thanks.</p>', '2009-01-14 18:26:58', 16, 37, 2, '', '', 0, 0, 1, NULL, '63.253.8.58'),
