(46, '<p>anyone looking for some sliding scale flute lessons? i&#39;d be so excited to be your tutor or flute playing companion! it&#39;s so fun! before you know it, you&#39;ll be covering jethro tull and impressing all your friends! i&#39;ve been playing for like 13 years, and it&#39;s really rad to find other people to play with. i picked up some begining flute books at the store, so all levels are welcome. come on down to georgetown &amp; we&#39;ll be playing dualing flutes before you know it. maybe like $5-20 half-hour, or $5-35&nbsp;full-hour sliding scale? yea, that sounds pretty good. let me know &amp; we&#39;ll figure out a time!! just send me an email, since i won&#39;t be checking this forum.</p>\r\n<p>love, jamie!</p>\r\n<p>littleprairie [at] riseup [dot] net</p>', '2009-08-23 20:19:16', 38, 99, 1, '', '', 0, 0, 1, 'a:2:{i:0;a:2:{s:2:"by";s:12:"arcticcircle";s:2:"at";i:1251076842;}i:1;a:2:{s:2:"by";s:12:"arcticcircle";s:2:"at";i:1251076879;}}', '98.246.106.29'),
