(49, '<p>Sliding scale -</p>\r\n<p>$5 - 20 for 1/2 hour</p>\r\n<p>$10 - 40 for full hour</p>\r\n<p>Beginning Piano lessons only.</p>\r\n<p>Beginning to Advanced Voice lessons.</p>\r\n<p>I have been playing organ/piano/keyboard for 21 years (but off&amp;on, so I can probably only help you with beginning lessons).&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>I have been singing for as long as I can remember (I&#39;m 29), but also received a BA in Classical Vocal Performance &amp; have been singing other types of music as well.&nbsp; My current project is called \\"World History\\" (<a href=\\"http://www.worldhistoryband.com\\" target="_blank">http://www.worldhistoryband.com</a>).&nbsp; If you can sing but want to expand your range, you can&#39;t sing but wish you could hold a tune, you&#39;re really good at singing along to your Modest Mouse albums but wish you could sing like Pavoratti, or whatever, I can try &amp; help.</p>\r\n<p>If you want to know more about music theory, that could happen with either of these lessons or I could also probably teach a lesson or two on that.</p>\r\n<p>Don&#39;t respond to this thread, as I probably won&#39;t check. Just send me an email at [ w o r l d h i s t o r y (at) r i s e&nbsp;u p (dot) n e t ]</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>All the best,</p>\r\n<p>NEIL</p>', '2009-08-30 00:13:24', 40, 99, 1, '', '', 0, 0, 1, NULL, '98.232.58.160');
