(50, '<p>My name is Justin and I play in a band called <a href=\\"http://www.myspace.com/merrychristmastheband\\" target="_blank">MERRY CHRISTMAS</a>&nbsp;(super gbv-influenced rock and roll/ slight pop punk) from Long Beach, CA, and we&#39;re having some troubles with setting up shows in the Northwest. We&#39;re doing a small coast trip with our friend Danny from the band <a href=\\"http://www.myspace.com/brownandbluemusic\\" target="_blank">BROWN AND BLUE</a>&nbsp;and he&#39;s going to be playing solo folk-y stuff. The date that we&#39;re looking for is November 4th OR 5th. The 4th we have listed for Olympia, but we&#39;re having no luck there. We&#39;re all nice guys, we prefer playing houses and simply asking for donations. We can cook and help clean up too! If there&#39;s ANYONE on here that can help, we would be ever so grateful. You can contact me at <a href="mailto:conway.justin@gmail.com" target="_blank">conway.justin@gmail.com</a> or from the myspace. Thanks guys, super sorry I had to be THAT guy.</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p><img title=\\"Cool\\" src=\\"http://www.seattlediy.com/wp-content/forum-smileys/sf-cool.gif\\" alt=\\"Cool\\" /></p>', '2009-09-06 20:08:29', 41, 210, 3, '', '', 0, 0, 1, NULL, '71.177.130.241'),
(51, '<p>we have a room opening up in my house for october 1st.&nbsp; The house is conveniently located on capitol hill near 15th Ave (625 Malden Ave E, to be exact).&nbsp; The room $800, it&#39;s sort of a master-bedroom suite/mother-in-law apt sort of thing with a bedroom, private bath, and private living room area. The living room and bedroom have separate entrances, so it could be two rooms at $400 each.&nbsp; There is a good basement for playing music, a small backyard with a small backyard garden, good roomates, etc.&nbsp; Feel free to forward this to anyone you know who might be interested, and email me at <a href=\\"mailto:jonah.byrne@gmail.com\\" target="_blank">jonah.byrne@gmail.com</a> if you have any questions or if you want to come look at the room.&nbsp; Thanks,<br /><span style=\\"color: #888888;\\"> jonah </span></p>', '2009-09-18 18:52:30', 42, 216, 1, '', '', 0, 0, 1, NULL, '24.18.177.197'),
