(69, '<p><strong><span style="color: #ff00ff;">Hi All <img title="Laugh" src="/wp-content/forum-smileys/sf-laugh.gif" alt="Laugh" />!!</span></strong></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>My name&#39;s Ashlee. I&#39;m 22 and currently interning on Bainbridge Island at <strong>YES</strong>! Magazine. I&#39;m <em>looking for a room</em> in <strong>SEATTLE</strong> this summer between May/June and August. Not too keen on the idea of heading back to PA anytime soon and would love to have a summer in the Pacific Northwest.</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>I love the idea of shared housing, community, etc., can pay affordable rent, do some work in exchange for rent, whatever. Can&#39;t wait to meet some awesome new people and explore the "mainland." I like to think of myself as open-minded, queer friendly, laid back, and responsible.</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>If you have a place, let me know! (ashleegreenbean@gmail.com).</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>TTFN,</p>\r\n<p>Ashlee</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />', '2010-03-28 22:03:46', 59, 309, 1, '', '', 0, 0, 1, NULL, '71.35.166.253'),
