(89, '<p>My time subletting at the Pet Seminary in Wallingford is coming to an end at the end of this month, I had plans for moving in with a friend but recently my plans have changed, and I think I&#39;m looking to live in another show house situation in Seattle!</p>\r\n<p>Right now I&#39;m paying 325 a month but I could probably go a bit higher if need be =).</p>\r\n<p>Feel free to give me a call if you have any questions, my phone number is 425-213-9260</p>\r\n<p>I&#39;m gr8 @ being a room8</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>-Ed</p>\r\n<br />', '2010-10-11 04:07:33', 75, 330, 1, '', '', 0, 0, 1, NULL, '184.78.197.212');
